room_title: Escape room "Operation: DB Cooper" by NW Escape Experience in Portland
review: The experience was beyond fun, staff was amazing. JESSE was a fantastic FBI agent for our DB Cooper adventure...We will be coming back.

room_title: Escape room "Operation: DB Cooper" by NW Escape Experience in Portland
review: We did the DB Cooper escape room and it was soooo much fun! Highly recommend for a fun date night, team building, or just friends' night out! Definitely coming back for the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Operation: DB Cooper" by NW Escape Experience in Portland
review: We found it to be fun, challenging, exciting and suspenseful. We highly recommend it for birthday fun or just out for a good time. We are looking forward to doing it again very soon.

room_title: Escape room "Operation: DB Cooper" by NW Escape Experience in Portland
review: My friends and I had an absolute blast! So well thought out, great decor to fit the theme, challenging puzzles and killer storyline! Highly recommend for any group for a fun evening!
